data.description: It's time to COME HOME to this beautiful house that sits within the Rocklin City limits. This highly sought after area offers space and comfort and allows for a family to live, laugh and enjoy entertaining inside and out.  This LEEd certified home has a tankless hot water heater, central vacuum, and wine Fridge.  The gorgeous pool will allow you to enjoy the hot summer days while the OWNED SOLAR will help manage and keep down the energy costs.  Brand new HVAC system recently put in. Downstairs In-law Suite.  Built-in surround sound in the living room and many more features that make this home a must see!  As a Whitney Ranch Homeowner you will have access to the beautiful 10,000 sq ft Ranch House Facility that boasts lots of amenities including a pool, Banquet ballroom, game room and recreational activities. The location could not be better as the proximity of Whitney High school and access to shopping and the freeway.  Do not hesitate to check this home out!
